title: Porsche IMSA GT3 Cup Challenge by Yokohama - Races 8 & 9, Mosport 2012
description: The Porsche IMSA GT3 Cup Challenge by Yokohama features drivers racing in the largest single-make series in North America. Powered by one of the world's most successful race cars, the Porsche 911 GT3 Cup car, the multi-class structure of the series teaches drivers essential skills for a career in the American Le Mans Series. The 2012 GT3 Cup Series is half way complete and now on it's second Canadian round at the famous Mosport circuit.
